*main.tex
	main TeX file
	
*main.pdf
	output PDF file
	
*main.zip
	a ZIP archive of everything required to generate `main.pdf`

*ducha.sty
	personal TeX settings by Duc A. Hoang (several packages will be loaded)

*vietex.sty
	created by [Nguyễn Hữu Điển](http://nhdien.wordpress.com/), for handling some fonts when typestting in Vietnamese, ignore it if you use English
	
*Makefile
	quickly compiling in GNU/Linux distributions with a simple `make` command
	
*make.bat
	quickly compiling in Windows CMD with a simple `make` command
	
*mplainnat.bst
	a custom Natbib's bibliography style, ignore it if you use BibLaTeX
	
*refs.bib
	a BibTeX file containing references
	
*Aalborg.sty
	Aalborg theme created by [Jesper Kjær Nielsen](http://www.sqrt-1.dk/)

*latexmkrc
	configure compiling with `latexmk`

*hus-beamer.sty
	Beamer theme with logo of [VNU-HUS](http://hus.vnu.edu.vn/)
